1 Employees Retirement System and State Police Retirement System have not received a
2 cost-of-living adjustment to their retirement allowances since fiscal year 2011-2012, an
3 emergency is declared to exist, and this Act takes effect upon its passage and approval by
4 the Governor or upon its otherwise becoming a law.
